@base_url = http://localhost:7292
@api_url = {{base_url}}/api/Users

### 1. Create a New User (POST)
# This uses the CreateUserRequest record structure
POST {{api_url}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane",
  "surname": "Doe",
  "email": "jane.doe@example.com"
}

###

### 2. Get User by ID (GET)
# Replace the GUID below with a real ID from your database
@userId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
GET {{api_url}}/{{userId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Get Selected Emails (GET)
GET {{api_url}}/emails
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Get Paged Users (GET)
# Demonstrates query parameters for index and size
GET {{api_url}}/paged?index=0&size=5
Accept: application/json